# A.R.C. runtime data — local to this clone, never commit.
# bodies.db / pipeline_events.db under tars/ hold raw request +
# response bodies (your source + model output); arc.db, reviews/ and
# progress/ are regenerable. Only the config template is shared —
# config.toml itself is your local environment routing.
*
